HEADWORD: Rete
<hw>Re"te</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., a net.]</ety>
<fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>A net or network; a plexus; particularly, a
network of blood vessels or nerves, or a part resembling a
network.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

